data.description: Nestled on a corner lot in the serene Western Plateau neighborhood this gem boasts the beauty of nature , trees both in the front and back yard. As you step into the inviting entryway you will be greeted by the warmth of brick flooring and elegant wainscoting. The kitchen features exquisite granite counter tops and a gleaming stainless steel stove.  The living room is a cozy retreat adorned with built in shelving, beams and a crackling fire place. I could go on but this delightful property is a true find and could very will be the one you have been searching for.
